Dave & Busters to open four units in 1998 . Dave & Busters Inc said Wednesday it plans to open four stores in 1998 and four additional units in 1999 . From the year 2000 onward , the chain plans to open five a year , David Corriveau , co - founder , told the Piper Jaffray investor conference here . Dave & Busters now has 10 restaurant - entertainment complexes in the United States and one in the United Kingdom . Corriveau said the company hopes to have seven in the United Kingdom by the year 2000 . ( ( Reuters Chicago Newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
